# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PUBLISHING POLICY ENFORCEMENT
# This repo is PUBLIC. These rules enforce ~/projects/PUBLISHING_POLICY.md.
# Everything not ignored here is visible to the world.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── PRIVATE: Methodology Documents (Policy: PRIVATE > Methodology) ──────
METHODOLOGY.md
METHODOLOGY-*.md
REVISED_METHODOLOGY.md
METHODOLOGY_ADDENDUM_*.md

# ── PRIVATE: Scoring & Evaluation (Policy: PRIVATE > Scoring) ───────────
SCORING_DIMENSIONS.md
EXPERIMENT_DESIGN.md
TRIAL_PROTOCOL.md
scorer/
trial*/DISCRETE_SCORES.json
trial*/*/DISCRETE_SCORES.json
trial*/SCORE_REPORT.md
trial*/RED_TEAM_REPORT.md
trial*/SCORE_RECONCILIATION.md
trial*/BUILD_REPORT.md
trial*/CALIBRATION_DELTA.md
trial*/NEW_FAILURE_MODES.md
trial*/REVISED_METHODOLOGY.md
trial*/SECURITY_SCAN.json
trial*/TRIAL_METADATA.json

# ── PRIVATE: Failure Mode Details (Policy: PRIVATE > Failure Modes) ─────
FAILURE-MODES.md
# The failure mode registry and detection rules are embedded in METHODOLOGY.md
# and scorer/ — both already ignored above.

# ── PRIVATE: Process & Protocol (Policy: PRIVATE > Process) ─────────────
# TRIAL_PROTOCOL.md already ignored above
# scorer/ already ignored above (contains verification/scoring logic)

# ── PRIVATE: Session Data (Policy: PRIVATE > Session Data) ──────────────
.claude/
**/PROMPT.md

# ── PRIVATE: Reports & Analysis ─────────────────────────────────────────
report/

# ── PRIVATE: Configuration & Secrets ────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# ── PUBLISH WITH REDACTION: phases.json ─────────────────────────────────
# phases.json is tracked but must NOT contain:
#   - dimensions_active (reveals rubric structure)
#   - convergence thresholds (numeric criteria)
#   - per-dimension or per-project score breakdowns
#   - scorer implementation details
# Public version contains only: phase, name, description, status, trial pass/fail, avg score

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# STANDARD IGNORES (not policy-related)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Dependencies
node_modules/
.pnpm-store/

# Docker volumes
docker-data/
postgres-data/

# Coverage output
coverage/
.nyc_output/

# Build output
dist/
.next/
.turbo/

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Trial build artifacts (large, reproducible)
trial*/*/node_modules/
trial*/*/dist/
trial*/*/coverage/
trial*/*/.next/
trial*/*/.turbo/
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/*.lock
**/CLAUDE.md
